quran[6{c,v,t}:
7,150,"idhar se moose ghusse aur ranj mein bhara howa apni qoum ki taraf palta atay hi is ne kaha"" bohat buri janshini ki tum logon ne mere baad! kya tum se itna sabr nah howa ke apne rab ke hukum ka intzaar kar letay ?"" aur tkhtyan pheink den aur apne bha yi ( haroon ) ke sir ke baal pakar kar usay khincha haroon ne kaha"" ae meri maa ke betay, inn logon ne mujhe daba liya aur qareeb tha ke mujhe maar daaltay pas to dushmanon ko mujh par hansnay ka mauqa nah day aur is zalim giroh ke sath mujhe nah shaamil kar """
7,151,"tab moose ne kaha"" ae rab, mujhe aur mere bhai ko maaf kar aur hamein apni rehmat mein daakhil farma, to sab se barh kar Raheem hai """
7,152,"( jawab mein irshad howa ke )"" jin logon ne bichhre ko mabood banaya woh zaroor apne rab ke ghazab mein girftar ho kar rahen ge aur duniya ki zindagi mein zaleel hon ge jhoot gharnay walon ko hum aisi hi saza dete hain"
7,153,"aur jo log buray amal karen phir tauba kar len aur imaan le ayen to yaqeenan iss tauba o imaan ke baad tera rab dar guzar aur reham frmane wala hai """
7,154,phir jab moose ka gussa thanda howa to is ne woh tkhtyan utha len jin ki tehreer mein hadaayat aur rehmat thi unn logon ke liye jo apne rab se drtay hain
7,155,"aur uss ne apni qoum ke sattar admion ko muntakhib kya taakay woh ( uss ke sath ) hamaray muqarrar kiye hue waqt par haazir hon jab inn logon ko aik sakht zalzalay ne aa pakra to moose ne arz kya"" ae mere sarkar, aap chahtay to pehlay hi inn ko aur mujhe halaak kar saktay thay kya aap uss qasoor mein jo hum mein se chand nadano-n ne kiya tha hum sab ko halaak kar den ge? yeh to aap ki daali hui aik azmaish thi jis ke zareya se aap jisay chahtay hain gumraahi mein mubtala kar dete hain aur jisay chahtay hain hadaayat bakhash dete hain hamaray sir parast to aap hi hain pas hamein maaf kar degiye aur hum par reham frmayie, aap sab se barh kar maaf frmane walay hain"
